  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">
      Check context. Output: "🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: STANDARD — Integration tests for Pillar 8 composition; no new code surface". Read project CLAUDE.md.
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Read TASK-INDEX.md; confirm 084 status is 🔲, deps 081/082/083 are ✅. Update `current-task.md`.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">
      Read CommandRouter.ts (080), SoftSlashRouter.ts (082), ReferenceResolver.ts (083). Identify the BFF chat-endpoint payload schema for mock fixtures.
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Author Composition Test Suite">
      Create `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/conversation/__tests__/composition.integration.test.ts`. Tests: (a) `/summarize #engagement-letter.docx` → payload has `commandIntent: 'summarize'` + `resolvedReferences: [{type:'file', canonicalId:..., displayName:'engagement-letter.docx'}]`; (b) `/draft response to @opposing-counsel about #motion-to-dismiss` → payload has `commandIntent: 'draft'` + 2 resolvedReferences; (c) NFR-11 regression: "summarize the engagement letter" (natural language) → payload has `commandIntent: null`, references = [].
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Build + Run Tests">
      Run `npm install --legacy-peer-deps --no-audit --no-fund` + `npm run test` against the new test file. Confirm all tests green.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
      Walk through every &lt;acceptance-criterion&gt; below.
    </step>
